Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.18,0:00:05.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}部員確實有六個了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.33,0:00:08.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}顧問是?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.47,0:00:11.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.08,0:00:15.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.27,0:00:24.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.54,0:00:25.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}老師也…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.23,0:00:28.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學園長接受了我們的申請
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.26,0:00:33.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喵喵社作為結女正式的社團被承認了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.99,0:00:34.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:35.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.79,0:00:41.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.40,0:00:47.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不擅長和動物打交道的愛理會加入喵喵社
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.89,0:00:49.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底使用了什麼魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.59,0:00:51.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:55.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然能都夠想像到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.09,0:00:57.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒錯

Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.40,0:02:35.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5\pos(1095,580)}{\pos(980,560)}{\3c&HB58E00&}{\fn方正综艺_GBK\fs40\fad(500,300)}黃昏色的鞦韆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.24,0:02:47.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接下來 該給松鼠餵食了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.90,0:02:49.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.50,0:02:52.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}向日葵的種子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:55.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}脂肪含量比較高 所以控制了量
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全按乾說的做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:00.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}很好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.82,0:03:04.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的就是那樣的地方無懈可擊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.34,0:03:06.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真不愧是安潔的主人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.31,0:03:09.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為他是我哥哥嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.92,0:03:26.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.58,0:03:30.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.14,0:03:33.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天羽前輩 打工結束了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.44,0:03:34.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.64,0:03:38.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起了 讓你替我照顧小熊喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.17,0:03:40.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.61,0:03:42.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多適應了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.64,0:03:43.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.45,0:03:45.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.36,0:03:47.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.93,0:03:51.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 瓜生明天有什麼安排嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.79,0:03:52.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}明天嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:56.13,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大概是在家呆著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.54,0:04:00.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那一起去各務賣場吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.99,0:04:03.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}購物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.66,0:04:05.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.63,0:04:11.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果我可以的話 很樂意
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:12.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.23,0:04:13.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:20.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個嗎 不 這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.66,0:04:23.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃覺得哪個更好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.20,0:04:23.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.81,0:04:26.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這件和這件衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.78,0:04:28.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你要去哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:33.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}各務商業街 陪天羽前輩去買東西
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.74,0:04:35.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.83,0:04:39.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}平常的就好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.64,0:04:41.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 平常穿的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.69,0:04:43.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.27,0:04:45.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.28,0:05:05.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼垃圾蟲會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.54,0:05:07.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾才是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:10.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我接下來要和美羽前輩去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.10,0:05:13.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 我也被前輩邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.15,0:05:18.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別胡說了 為什麼美羽前輩會邀請你這樣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.70,0:05:22.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉 我來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:27.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩 一點都沒遲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.51,0:05:29.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}離約定時間還有10分鐘呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.64,0:05:33.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了 比起這個聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.69,0:05:37.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這只垃圾蟲胡言亂語 說被美羽前輩邀請
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:40.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我也邀請了瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.85,0:05:43.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}想著大家一起去購物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這樣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:52.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}既然成為正式的社團 想著該買些不足的物品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:55.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:06:00.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}前輩 手會腐爛的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:03.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生的手真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.78,0:06:18.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小熊貓 別弄壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.30,0:06:21.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}太好了 看起來它很喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.69,0:06:26.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有買回來的價值呢 天羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.70,0:06:28.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯? 瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.03,0:06:30.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:34.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們都已經是同一個社團了 不用那麼拘束的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.02,0:06:36.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫我美羽就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.65,0:06:38.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:42.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣絕對不行 美羽前輩的名字會被玷污的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:45.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 叫美羽前輩怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:50.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 那我叫你新吾可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.58,0:06:52.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}當然 請多多關照
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.69,0:06:53.41,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.72,0:06:55.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請多多關照 新吾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.97,0:07:02.02,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是噩夢啊 居然從美羽前輩口中聽到那個惡魔的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪也給自己想個暱稱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.90,0:07:06.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:12.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比如 紗凪親呀 紗凪炭呀 紗凪凪之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.53,0:07:14.08,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.44,0:07:15.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 一點都不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.03,0:07:17.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}絕對不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.06,0:07:21.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我沒有打算和那傢夥親近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.85,0:07:26.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像我也被瀨名說過呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.16,0:07:29.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我可沒有愛理那麼天真
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.78,0:07:30.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是的 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:36.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個 美羽前輩喝可可吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.96,0:07:39.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.23,0:07:43.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}放口袋裡暖和了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.55,0:07:46.28,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.09,0:07:50.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像戰國武將一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.20,0:07:52.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可沒有垃圾蟲的份
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:56.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那新吾也喝點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.33,0:07:59.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 不可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.53,0:08:01.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 垃圾蟲 為什麼接著了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.69,0:08:03.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不… 美羽前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.84,0:08:07.11,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 這個變成間接接吻了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.58,0:08:10.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是新吾的話 我不在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:11.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.36,0:08:14.16,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請在意一些
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.45,0:08:17.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 我不會對其他男人這麼做的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:18.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其他男人是?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.28,0:08:23.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你這樣的傢夥…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:26.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.04,0:08:29.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.61,0:08:31.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.54,0:08:35.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我的錯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.27,0:08:39.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 錯的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.92,0:08:40.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}肯定是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.89,0:09:00.54,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.99,0:09:07.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理 去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.98,0:09:11.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 你怎麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.99,0:09:13.73,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:20.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要喝可可嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.57,0:09:29.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然有點涼了 剩了出來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.93,0:09:45.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 雖然說是來後山
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.88,0:09:48.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可都到深山了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.95,0:09:54.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}櫻乃 要喝嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:57.70,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝 幫了我大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:00.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}愛理怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.92,0:10:03.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}現在還不用
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.35,0:10:22.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好了 回家去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.72,0:10:27.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:34.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}快點回去 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.44,0:10:40.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要小心點了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:10:59.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要認真消毒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.79,0:11:06.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看著籠子變空 覺得有些孤獨了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.62,0:11:11.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋 美羽前輩可是為了讓這裡的籠子裡全部變空而努力著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.85,0:11:14.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.48,0:11:16.62,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾不也哭了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.99,0:11:21.59,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接受這傢夥的手帕 真的人生的污點
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:26.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}天變冷了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.77,0:11:29.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}手沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.56,0:11:30.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.38,0:11:32.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}燒傷的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.54,0:11:36.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事的 本來就不是什麼嚴重的燒傷
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.08,0:11:44.45,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在這不長的時間裡 發生了不少事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.89,0:11:51.12,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再重申一次 現在我還沒有認可你是正式的部員
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:54.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼做你才能認可我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.87,0:11:56.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你變成女人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.36,0:12:01.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}或者不進入美羽前輩半徑10米範圍內就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.84,0:12:04.50,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果做不到的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.52,0:12:10.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓就用實力證明給我看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.05,0:12:12.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.71,0:12:27.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}-早上好 新吾\N早上好 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.41,0:12:29.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.95,0:12:31.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來得好晚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.19,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你以為自己是身份顯要 能遲到嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.98,0:12:38.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我去處理下外面的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.95,0:12:40.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我陪你去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.38,0:12:45.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也是 櫻乃一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:47.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:52.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}外面的事 有那麼多嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.50,0:12:52.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.13,0:12:54.01,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好痛 痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.43,0:12:55.10,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.71,0:12:58.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 有點落枕了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.70,0:13:00.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.01,0:13:05.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡應該有我之前做的藥膏
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.45,0:13:06.84,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係 也不是很痛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.52,0:13:13.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這可是為了讓你全身都有藥膏的味道 美羽前輩就會遠離你的作戰呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.17,0:13:17.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣的作戰還是保密的好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.92,0:13:26.11,Comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓜生~...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.39,0:13:22.60,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:23.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.05,0:13:27.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.04,0:13:35.87,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哇 好難聞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.27,0:13:38.52,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這樣是女人都不會靠近你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.84,0:13:39.65,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}活該
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:43.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也去幫忙外面的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.56,0:13:46.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係的 你好好休息吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.94,0:13:49.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}脖子不能活動 幫不上忙的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.97,0:13:52.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且還有藥膏的味道
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.50,0:13:54.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和作戰目標一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.34,0:14:04.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上好 一大早又是社團活動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.90,0:14:05.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.78,0:14:10.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}最近我都不能和你還有小櫻乃一起上學 都想哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.05,0:14:13.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}照顧動物 很早就得開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.39,0:14:17.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且 聽說你還交到女朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.43,0:14:19.34,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 女朋友?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.63,0:14:21.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是和乾在交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.62,0:14:27.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我一直以為你喜歡年紀比你大的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.33,0:14:29.77,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}等等 為什麼會變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.14,0:14:33.81,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瀨名和小櫻乃說的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.66,0:14:36.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是這樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.72,0:14:43.36,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哥哥 連我都不告訴太見外了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.82,0:14:44.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是 不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.91,0:14:49.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說你是聽誰說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:51.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是聽愛理說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.34,0:14:55.09,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是聽安潔說的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.27,0:14:57.05,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.91,0:15:04.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謠言被傳播得就是快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}傳出去的是安潔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.86,0:15:10.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}為什麼要去傳播這樣無憑無據的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:13.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}安潔是聽美羽前輩說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:16.47,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽前輩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:21.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓主人的戀情悄然孕育萌發也是女僕的職責
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.33,0:15:28.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以… 我們早上讓主人和紗凪兩個人獨處了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.23,0:15:30.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後兩個人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.50,0:15:39.49,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起 我不是那麼打算才說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.09,0:15:44.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為討厭男人的小紗凪經常和新吾說話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.95,0:15:47.40,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以想讓大家溫柔地守護著
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.94,0:15:51.35,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那為什麼會變成兩個人在交往了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:55.99,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謠言本來就是會被不斷加工潤色的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.26,0:15:58.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別說得像他人的事一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.50,0:15:59.78,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那本來就是他人的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.50,0:16:04.80,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 大家聚在一起說什麼事情呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.34,0:16:07.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:09.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}小紗凪也一起聊天吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:14.31,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不了 我只是在找瓜生而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.78,0:16:15.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.20,0:16:20.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}早上忘記還給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.64,0:16:23.27,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:27.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那我去社團了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:35.75,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 大家一句話都不說
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.38,0:16:37.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.26,0:16:46.98,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}乾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.54,0:16:51.79,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了 有藥膏的味道別靠近我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.58,0:17:01.66,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}開玩笑的 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.57,0:17:10.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}變成大人 這些就不能玩了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:11.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:19.42,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這種時候 就沒有在背後推一下 懂得情調的男人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.06,0:17:21.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果是我 你會厭惡的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.37,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你不是很清楚嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:31.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 乾
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.08,0:17:33.94,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個已經沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.28,0:17:34.82,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.26,0:17:38.85,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫我乾 感覺很不好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.52,0:17:40.72,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}叫紗凪就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.50,0:17:44.71,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}作為交換 我會叫你新吾的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.49,0:17:47.32,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.70,0:17:48.46,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.08,0:17:52.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.39,0:17:53.56,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不用加敬語
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.24,0:17:57.03,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就叫你紗凪了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.07,0:17:59.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.18,0:18:02.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 你有什麼事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.23,0:18:07.61,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 啊 雖然很難說出口
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.01,0:18:08.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.15,0:18:13.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家似乎都誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.03,0:18:15.22,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}關於我們的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.07,0:18:16.88,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誤會?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.83,0:18:23.76,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}應該怎麼說的 說我和紗凪在交往什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.78,0:18:32.14,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼 那是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.30,0:18:33.15,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.59,0:18:38.39,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那些人是笨蛋吧 誰會去和垃圾蟲交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.13,0:18:42.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再說 我對男人根本不感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.46,0:18:44.29,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:47.55,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且 對你也造成困擾了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:48.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.09,0:18:53.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你喜歡美羽前輩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.38,0:18:54.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.82,0:19:00.83,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是 我絕對不會把美羽前輩交給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.25,0:19:05.64,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}無論怎麼看 你和美羽前輩都不般配
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.96,0:19:11.91,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}總之 謠言我會去否定的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.12,0:19:13.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}讓它完全消失
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.96,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 幫了大忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.62,0:19:20.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但你也不能向美羽前輩下手
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.08,0:19:25.23,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒關係 正如紗凪所說的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.24,0:19:31.20,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我和美羽前輩就算地球倒轉 也不可能在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.90,0:19:34.44,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.29,0:19:36.90,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.21,0:19:38.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.57,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不是說有味道 不要靠近我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.31,0:19:46.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.72,0:20:29.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我做了對新吾和小紗凪不好的事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.98,0:20:33.38,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會 誰都可能會有誤解的時候的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.02,0:20:36.53,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我是覺得你們很般配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.96,0:20:37.89,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}完全不是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.38,0:20:39.24,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會和乾...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:43.95,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪完全沒把我放在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.94,0:20:45.68,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}紗凪?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.39,0:20:49.33,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她讓我這麼稱呼她的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.91,0:20:52.63,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.00,0:20:57.07,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 美羽前輩今天不用去打工嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.48,0:21:02.48,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也不能總是拜託大家照看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.77,0:21:03.74,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.86,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反倒是前輩 工作太辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.42,0:21:08.67,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會的 我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.15,0:21:13.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這小傢夥的傷 什麼時候能癒合呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.88,0:21:17.58,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 還要再過一段時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.98,0:21:21.43,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}瓜生…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:25.04,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要是能早點放歸山林就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.91,0:21:26.51,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.25,0:21:33.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是… 要大家都不在了 也會覺得孤獨的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.01,0:21:37.92,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒 哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.20,0:21:43.18,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}美羽… 前輩

Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.94,0:23:29.00,TEXT,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}新吾 新吾
